            "stanza_text": "Souffle, bise ! tombe à flots, pluie !\nDans mon palais tout noir de suie,\nJe ris de la pluie et du vent ;\nEn attendant que l'hiver fuie,\nJe reste au coin du feu, rêvant."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "C'est moi qui suis l'esprit de l'âtre !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Le gaz, de sa langue bleuâtre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Lèche plus doucement le bois ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "La fumée, en filet d'albâtre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Monte et se contourne à ma voix.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est moi qui suis l'esprit de l'âtre !\nLe gaz, de sa langue bleuâtre,\nLèche plus doucement le bois ;\nLa fumée, en filet d'albâtre,\nMonte et se contourne à ma voix."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "La bouilloire rit et babille ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "La flamme aux pieds d'argent sautille",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "En accompagnant ma chanson ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "La bûche de duvet s'habille ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "La sève bout dans le tison.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La bouilloire rit et babille ;\nLa flamme aux pieds d'argent sautille\nEn accompagnant ma chanson ;\nLa bûche de duvet s'habille ;\nLa sève bout dans le tison."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Le soufflet au râle asthmatique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Me fait entendre sa musique ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Le tourne-broche aux dents d'acier",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Mêle au concerto domestique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Le tic-tac de son balancier.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le soufflet au râle asthmatique\nMe fait entendre sa musique ;\nLe tourne-broche aux dents d'acier\nMêle au concerto domestique\nLe tic-tac de son balancier."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Les étincelles réjouies,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "En étoiles épanouies,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Vont et viennent, croisant dans l'air",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Les salamandres éblouies,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Au ricanement grêle et clair.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les étincelles réjouies,\nEn étoiles épanouies,\nVont et viennent, croisant dans l'air\nLes salamandres éblouies,\nAu ricanement grêle et clair."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Du fond de ma cellule noire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Quand Berthe vous conte une histoire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Le Chaperon ou l'Oiseau bleu,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "C'est moi qui soutiens sa mémoire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "C'est moi qui fais taire le feu.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Du fond de ma cellule noire,\nQuand Berthe vous conte une histoire,\nLe Chaperon ou l'Oiseau bleu,\nC'est moi qui soutiens sa mémoire,\nC'est moi qui fais taire le feu."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "J'étouffe le bruit monotone",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Du rouet qui grince et bourdonne ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "J'impose silence au matou ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Les heures s'en vont, et personne",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "N'entend le timbre du coucou.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J'étouffe le bruit monotone\nDu rouet qui grince et bourdonne ;\nJ'impose silence au matou ;\nLes heures s'en vont, et personne\nN'entend le timbre du coucou."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Pendant la nuit et la journée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Je chante sous la cheminée ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Dans mon langage de grillon",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "J'ai, des rebuts de son aînée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Souvent consolé Cendrillon.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pendant la nuit et la journée,\nJe chante sous la cheminée ;\nDans mon langage de grillon\nJ'ai, des rebuts de son aînée,\nSouvent consolé Cendrillon."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Le renard glapit dans le piége ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Le loup, hurlant de faim, assiège",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "La ferme au milieu des grands bois ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Décembre met, avec sa neige,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Des chemises blanches aux toits.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le renard glapit dans le piége ;\nLe loup, hurlant de faim, assiège\nLa ferme au milieu des grands bois ;\nDécembre met, avec sa neige,\nDes chemises blanches aux toits."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Allons, fagot, pétille et flambe ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Courage ! farfadet ingambe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Saule, bondis plus haut encor ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Salamandre, montre ta jambe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Lève en dansant ton jupon d'or.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Allons, fagot, pétille et flambe ;\nCourage ! farfadet ingambe,\nSaule, bondis plus haut encor ;\nSalamandre, montre ta jambe,\nLève en dansant ton jupon d'or."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Quel plaisir ? prolonger sa veille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Regarder la flamme vermeille",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Prenant à deux bras le tison,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "A tous les bruits prêter l'oreille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Entendre vivre la maison !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quel plaisir ? prolonger sa veille,\nRegarder la flamme vermeille\nPrenant à deux bras le tison,\nA tous les bruits prêter l'oreille,\nEntendre vivre la maison !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Tapi dans sa niche bien chaude,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Sentir l'hiver qui pleure et rôde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Tout blême et le nez violet,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Tâchant de s'introduire en fraude",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Par quelque fente du volet !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tapi dans sa niche bien chaude,\nSentir l'hiver qui pleure et rôde,\nTout blême et le nez violet,\nTâchant de s'introduire en fraude\nPar quelque fente du volet !"
        },
